Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I won again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...Lieselotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto! Hey, Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, he has a pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's covered in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was splattered on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:00:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's carry him to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:01:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We should at least have the infirmary doctor look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.40,0:01:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Step away from the Valvrave.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Valv-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the name of that ridiculous robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You JIOR people named it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't Sakimori Academy students?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, Dorssians!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a ventilation duct over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, L-elf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why turn your gun on us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A-drei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.30,0:02:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-vier! Watch the perimeter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,H-neun, let's call headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save us? Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I got into this body, but I'm Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Get real!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell should I hand over my cell to you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I run this school, you Dorssian dicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I not gonna let you act like you own—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in resisting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The JIOR homeland has already surrendered unconditionally!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:28.30,Alt,,0,0,0,,Surrendered?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it again so it'll sink through those peace-softened skulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:32.01,Alt,,0,0,0,,It wasn't just here that was attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The country of JIOR no longer exists!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is now an incorporated territory of Greater Dorssia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock-paper-scissors! Rock! Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock! Rock! Rock! Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really you in there, Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have mixed feelings that it took a game to prove it's me, but yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's really you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty hazy, but I remember climbing down from that robot, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you even fired a gun before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Its just like amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you lose your memory, you can still talk or use a phone or whatever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means that the owner of this body fought on a daily basis?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this guy's story?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's retrieve Haruto's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point. This is freaking me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take back that robot and smash those Dorssian bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, it doesn't even come close to balancing out what I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people killed Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The JIOR government has agreed to an unconditional surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The annexation of JIOR seems to have been successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir. We have finished neutralizing the enemy's combat potential in Module 77.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Displacement of the JIOR populace is currently underway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were able to secure the primary strategic objective with relatively little damage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its pilot is still unconscious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a student at that school that was shown on the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And what of L-elf?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A-About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf turned traitor, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}L-elf injured A-drei and remains at large.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cause, unknown.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe someone from the Karlstein Agency would turn traitor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is the first blemish on the reputation of the Perfection Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who goes there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that? This is war, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But you—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't get to kill Shoko and then plead for their own lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Inzukua-senpai, you and the girls stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This next part is going to involve killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto, what's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't at least avenge her, I could never forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is its engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Its way too small. You saw how much power it put out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a neutral country like JIOR doing with tech like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This design is based on a totally new line of thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,These are radiator fins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, they were giving off smoke in the battle yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did they make it humanoid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The real mystery is why the frame changed color like it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The wounds... They're healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!I guess this thing doesn't handle like a bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold out your hands. I'll tie you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf turned up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir! The primary strategic objective has been stolen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just recreate what you did the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And this will turn me back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it usually works in the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something I can do, so I guess I have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back! I'm in my own body!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. We're both back to normal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorssians go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Point-blank fire would be unwise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Attitude control! Right roll 15!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This guy is an amateur?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's use this chance to leave the Module.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We can rendezvous with our forces outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is— We're in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no surface, how do I—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course there isn't! We're in space!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A single unit can't possibly win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't block my view!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the light that was in the reports?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too hard, A-drei. Your injuries aren't healed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A-drei! Ideal, box out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Blitzendegen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Blitzendegen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-vier, box out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The pride of the Dorssian army, the heavy strategic weapon Ideal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how we could fight ARUS as more than equals though Dorssia was weaker as a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That attack... It's A-drei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that number mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If it reaches 100, it stops moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep it running too long, it overheats.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stopped moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Signal them that you're standing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of Rukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no wounds...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}L-elf! Why did you shoot me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You traitor!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned traitor? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You shot one of your own people. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't shoot anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much for turning traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to see what it was like to fight you, L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Back off, Q-vier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one to settle things with L-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you people do to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, shoot A-drei? Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:15:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This ringtone, it's—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto? Haruto, is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice... Shoko? Is it really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In the dirt. It looks like the whole car got buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:24.71,Alt,,0,0,0,,Really...? So that's what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made certain that he was dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But compared to his clothes, the damage to his body is nonexistent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:32.01,Alt,,0,0,0,,What a relief... I'm so glad you're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my battery's about to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading straight back. We can just talk face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no memory of shooting A-drei.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I have injuries I don't remember getting...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened to my body while I was blacked out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was I controlled? By who?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko, when I get back, let's pick up our talk where we left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The one in front of the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise! Because I'm heading back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It started!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stopped again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why now?! Shoko is alive! I promised her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I'd come back for her! Why now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't end here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Work, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,41 Hertz, 30 micropascals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The engine sound is still running.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The medical box on the seat back shows signs of being rewritten
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so all the text would be in the same sans serif style.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clear that this cockpit's designer had a pathological attention to detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But look at the scale of the heat capacity gauge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The next unit after 100 is 666.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I find it hard to believe that such a designer would use a number that has no significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would it do this while there are so many alerts going off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What comes after 666?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll start by ripping off your arms and legs!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't die. I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Shoko is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender, L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a promise to Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's I'd come back to her alive, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm gonna—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't like the looks of that! Get clear, A-drei!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It committed harakiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gather remaining forces! Regroup, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The ARUS fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They're showing up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall back! It's time to retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-vier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we... saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, were saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that I killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So why are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I shoot A-drei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I remember doing it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You did all of it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They were telling the truth! You're piloting a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's big!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. You sent them to look for me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, it was no big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, about picking up where we left off?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the shrine? We were interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, I think you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your T-shirt is lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd always thought so. "Who makes a T-shirt like that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a limited edition! And it's signed by the creator's mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?! I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking all serious, and that's what you say to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:22:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your lack of fashion sense is that serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The bathroom! I've been holding it in for hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.68,0:22:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross! You're a louse!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell, man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on... What else could I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been turned into a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the right to tell her how I really feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.85,0:24:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, episode 3. "L-elf's Prophesy."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.73,0:24:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Valvrave the Liberator; it's the system to reveal the truth of the world.
